These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-4-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, tiparillo, baccarat, old-henry, dannemann, dunhill, game
The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker, electrician, lawyer, mechanic, police-officer, scientist
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, tea, milk, fanta, soy-milk, coffee
There are 7 different favourite colors: fuchsia, chestnut, green, ivory, yellow, brown, white
 1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 2. the person who likes white is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the mechanic is the person who likes brown##1
 4. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who likes fuchsia is the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is the dunhill-smoker##1
 7. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the accountant##3
 8. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
 9. the person who likes white is in an odd position##4
10. the scientist is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
11. the police-officer is the baccarat-smoker##1
12. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
13. the mechanic is on the right of the dressmaker##1
14. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
15. the baccarat-smoker is between the accountant and the person who likes yellow##2
16. the police-officer is on the left of the electrician##1
17. the old-henry-smoker is the person who likes yellow##1
18. the lawyer is on the far left or far right##3
19. the police-officer is on the left or right of the accountant##3
20. the police-officer is the baccarat-smoker##1
21. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
22. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
23. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the accountant##3
24. the person who likes white is on the far left or far right##3
25. the mechanic is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
26. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |       3        |       4       |     5      |     6      |      7       |
| Cigar        | tiparillo | dunhill     | baccarat           | old-henry          | dannemann  | game | aristoff         |
| Job         | scientist  | accountant | police-officer | electrician   | dressmaker | mechanic   | lawyer       |
| Beverage       | fanta   | 7up  | tea        | soy-milk | iced-tea   | milk    | coffee |
| Color   | white        | ivory       | fuchsia           | yellow         | green     | brown       | chestnut    |

